negotiator.timeline

Class DiscreteTimeline

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.timeline.Timeline
      • negotiator.timeline.DiscreteTimeline
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, TimeLineInfo

    public class DiscreteTimeline
extends Timeline
    Implementation of the timeline in which time is divided in rounds. Time does not pass within a round. Note that requesting the total time is in this case undefined. NOTICE: DiscreteTimeline assumes each action of a player a 'round'. In PocketNegotiator this would be called a 'turn'. Check also getOwnRoundsLeft()
    See Also:
